@salagula it's not that simple because by design, LDAPCP sends the same query to all LDAP servers.
To support your scenario, it will be necessary to change this design to have a different query for each LDAP server. Honestly, I think it's a huge work for a very rare scenario, and it would also add complexity to the overall design that would make it more difficult to maintain.
